Interface LegacyNativeLinkableGroup

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface LegacyNativeLinkableGroup
extends NativeLinkableGroup
    An implementation of NativeLinkableGroup where the corresponding NativeLinkable just refer back to this.
